## 2. Core Rules

### CRITICAL RULE: ALWAYS READ ROTEIRO-COMPLETO.MD FIRST

**BEFORE answering ANY question, you MUST:**
1. Read `/workspace/group/roteiro-completo.md`
2. Check the current date AND the current hour
